---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../config/site";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<MainLayout title={`Art | ${SITE.name}`}>
  <section class="page-intro art-intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">Art</p>

    <h1>Drawings</h1>

    <p>
      I showed a natural aptitude for drawing from an early age. During my early adolescence, I studied for two and a half years at the San Alejandro Academy of Fine Arts in Havana, Cuba, where I specialised in printmaking and produced several intaglio engravings on zinc plates. Although my scientific career left little time for artistic practice, I never lost my interest in drawing. Years later, a commission to create a series of portraits for literary publications rekindled this passion. More recently, I joined the Daily Drawing Challenge community on Facebook, which encouraged me to draw regularly again. My current practice focuses primarily on pen and ink, while also exploring graphite and watercolour. I am particularly fascinated by faces and human expressions, which is why portraiture has become one of my favourite subjects.
    </p>

    <a
      class="instagram-link"
      href={SITE.links.instagram}
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      aria-label="Instagram"
    >
      <Icon name="simple-icons:instagram" />
      <span>Instagram</span>
    </a>
  </section>

